14 rebounds as the Dallas Mavericks won their fifth straight game, 92-81 over
the Portland Trail Blazers on Tuesday night. Erick Strickland had 18 points and
Shawn Bradley scored 12 to help the Mavericks win for the seventh time in their
last eight games.
</P>
