42. Talk-show host Conan O'Brien is 37. Actress Jane Leeves is 37.
Actor Eric McCormack (''Will and Grace'') is 37. Actress Maria
Bello is 33. Musician Greg Eklund of Everclear is 30. Actress
Melissa Joan Hart is 24.
</P>
